{"tid":1817082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 見到好多人排老麥 想講","createTime":"2020-01-08T18:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T18:50:02.000Z","uid":128088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c91d265acbfa3116507b4180c59b27201e6393c","tid":1817082,"uid":128088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"越多人排我越開心 越興奮<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">小弟其實係開餐廳 <br />\n從以往經驗 <br />\n臨過新年 <br />\n飲食業生意係全年<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最好</span></strong> <br />\n一般企業冇可能 起依段時間出promotion<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n香港。黃 藍 豬 <br />\n比例係4  3  3<br />\n<br />\n各位唔洗咁驚訝<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解仲咁多人排</span></strong><br />\n反而應該<span style=\"color: brown;\">開心</span><br />\n令所有<span style=\"color: blue;\">廢藍</span>淨係幫襯某一食肆<br />\n變相佢地<span style=\"color: blue;\">鬼打鬼咁</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論係 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">越多藍既大企業出promotion吸客<br />\n就越多中立 or 藍小店收皮</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">堅持黃色經濟圈 加油 各位手足</span>"},{"pid":"aedcada15c6835c5baa8faa0c504909a9246110e","tid":1817082,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:50:02.000Z","msg":"最好就藍既大企業同小店一齊收皮<br />\n<br />\n我已經一年冇食過香港M記，但得我一個冇用。最麻煩就係諗唔到有咩代替品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}